veropkg - Veronic Linux Package Manager
Cross Platform Production Prototype

Features:
- Dependency resolution
- Circular dependency detection
- Atomic database writes
- Cross platform file locking
- Safe extraction
- Transaction rollback
- Package install and removal
- Repository sync
- Sandbox execution
- Auto dependency cleanup
- SHA256 verification
- Safe install roots
- Basic self tests
"""

